high_descs: Turn right, proceed to tub.  Turn left to face table.
Pick up soap from table, directly in front of candle.
Back up slightly from table.
Open top drawer of table, put soap in left hand side of drawer.  Close drawer.
Turn around, proceed to green sink.
Pick up soap from inside sink.
Turn around, proceed to table.
Open drawer, place soap in drawer directly to the right of the other soap.  Close drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap to a single drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go to the bathtub, hang a left, go to the black table.
Pick up the bar of soap that is on the table.
Turn around, go forward, turn around to face the black table.
Put the bar of soap inside the drawer of the black table on the left side.
Turn around and head to the sink across the room.
Pick up the bar of soap that is in the sink.
Turn around go forward to the black table.
Put the bar of soap inside the drawer of the black table, to the right of the other bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap inside a drawer.

high_descs: Go to the small black table
Pick up a bar of soap from the table
Turn around and face the table
Put the bar of soap in the table drawer
Go to the sink
Pick up the bar of soap from the sink
Go to the black table
Put the soap in the table drawer
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap to a table drawer
